column5: Here's some pics from our trip to Lower Buckhorn the last week of June 2007. We'll be back up at Beachwood Resort the last week of June this year. Note: all fish in these pictures were released. For the week, we kept 1 walleye to eat (not pictured) and everything else went back in the lake.  Tom
Nice mixed bag you got there.  thanks for sharing.  reefrunner
Looks like you had a good time.  Well done.  Entropy
nice pics, hope this season fares you well too
Nice pics. Won't be long now.
NICE horizontal holds on them Muskie! And the other "baitfish" as well!  Thanks for sharing and more importantly for releasing them!
Those are some nice fish. Just a few more weeks now! Thanks for sharing.
